flowchart TD
    Internet([Internet])
    CF[CloudFront + WAF<br/>bot · rate · geo rules]
    BFF[SvelteKit UI / BFF]
    Pub["auth-api public :7011<br/>ECS Fargate (deploy/cdk/)"]
    Priv["auth-api private :7012<br/>VPC only"]
    SM[(Secrets Manager<br/>JWT keyset · client registry)]
    Redis[(ElastiCache Redis<br/>OTP · challenges · JTI denylist)]
    DDB[(DynamoDB<br/>banned customers)]
    Customer[customer-api<br/>identity · passkey creds]
    Comms[comms-api<br/>OTP email delivery]
    Services[other Komodo services<br/>verify-only via JWKSVerifier]

    Internet --> CF --> BFF
    BFF -->|"/v1/oauth/token · /v1/otp/* · /v1/passkeys/*<br/>/.well-known/jwks.json"| Pub
    Pub <-. one image, two binaries .-> Priv
    Services -->|"client_credentials (WithServiceAuth)"| Pub
    Services -->|introspect · validate| Priv
    Services -. JWKS fetch (cached by kid) .-> Pub
    Pub --> SM
    Pub --> Redis
    Pub --> DDB
    Pub --> Customer
    Pub --> Comms
    Priv --> SM
    Priv --> Redis
    Priv --> Customer
